verses.verse: Oh <S%H3212>come<s%>, let us <S%H7442>sing<s%> unto <S%H3068>Jehovah<s%>; Let us make a joyful <S%H7321>noise<s%> to the <S%H6697>rock<s%> of our <S%H3468>salvation<s%>.
Let us <S%H6923>come<s%> before his <S%H6440>presence<s%> with <S%H8426>thanksgiving<s%>; Let us make a joyful <S%H7321>noise<s%> unto him with <S%H2158>psalms<s%>.
For <S%H3068>Jehovah<s%> is a <S%H1419>great<s%> <S%H410>God<s%>, And a <S%H1419>great<s%> <S%H4428>King<s%> above all <S%H410>gods<s%>.
In his <S%H3027>hand<s%> are the deep <S%H4278>places<s%> of the <S%H776>earth<s%>; The <S%H8443>heights<s%> of the mountains are his <S%H2022>also<s%>.
The <S%H3220>sea<s%> is <S%H6213>his<s%>, and he made <S%H3027>it<s%>; And his hands <S%H3335>formed<s%> the dry <S%H3006>land<s%>.
Oh <S%H935>come<s%>, let us <S%H7812>worship<s%> and bow <S%H3766>down<s%>; Let us <S%H1288>kneel<s%> <S%H6440>before<s%> <S%H3068>Jehovah<s%> our <S%H6213>Maker<s%>:

For he is our <S%H430>God<s%>, And we are the <S%H5971>people<s%> of his <S%H4830>pasture<s%>, and the <S%H6629>sheep<s%> of his <S%H3027>hand<s%>. <S%H3117>To-day<s%>, oh that ye would <S%H8085>hear<s%> his <S%H6963>voice<s%>!
Harden <S%H7185><s%> not your <S%H3824>heart<s%>, as at <S%H4808>Meribah<s%>, As in the <S%H3117>day<s%> of <S%H4531>Massah<s%> in the <S%H4057>wilderness<s%>;
When your <S%H1>fathers<s%> <S%H5254>tempted<s%> <S%H974>me<s%>, Proved <S%H7200>me<s%>, and saw my <S%H6467>work<s%>.

Forty <S%H705><s%> <S%H8141>years<s%> long was I <S%H6962>grieved<s%> with that <S%H1755>generation<s%>, And <S%H559>said<s%>, It is a <S%H5971>people<s%> that do <S%H8582>err<s%> in their <S%H3824>heart<s%>, And they have not <S%H3045>known<s%> my <S%H1870>ways<s%>:
Wherefore I <S%H7650>sware<s%> in my <S%H639>wrath<s%>, That they should not <S%H935>enter<s%> into my <S%H4496>rest<s%>.
